3cdb267c-02ee-4684-bfb8-d208fa579b98.title: Witch
3cdb267c-02ee-4684-bfb8-d208fa579b98.text: Hello there, deary. Don't worry; I'm friendly.

c9a7ef84-e293-4d9e-9b71-4c995cf5e7f5.title: <player>
c9a7ef84-e293-4d9e-9b71-4c995cf5e7f5.text:
You look very familiar but I can't remember chatting to
you before.

c30b34e2-06d2-4ef9-8949-20b027bc5631.title: Witch
c30b34e2-06d2-4ef9-8949-20b027bc5631.text:
Well, my sisters used to live here but folk kept on
killing them. A terrible affair, it was. I knew that no one
would want to kill a chatty old dear like me, though.

ee14c8ca-7b43-4188-b823-1699be3a000e.title: Witch
ee14c8ca-7b43-4188-b823-1699be3a000e.text:
We still have a terrible problem with local louts, though.
Poisoning my fish, spilling my compost all over the place
and causing a nuisance for the dear count.

21d50a88-98b2-4192-aca6-f7fb2e8d6de2.title: Witch
21d50a88-98b2-4192-aca6-f7fb2e8d6de2.text:
I'm sure a nice young sort like you won't be any
trouble, though. In any case, the Professor will soon
share the secret of chickenisation with me... Not that I'd
use it these days of course.

02b1117b-75df-42c8-a7f6-3e04e23366c9.title: Witch
02b1117b-75df-42c8-a7f6-3e04e23366c9.text:
Hello, hello, my poppet. What brings you to my little
room?

d601b9ce-2388-4fc9-b344-9e908ad0483b.title: <player>
d601b9ce-2388-4fc9-b344-9e908ad0483b.text:
Ava told me to ask you about making magnets.
Something about natural fields and other stuff. Sounded
like she needed a farmer, to be honest.

b4c814d8-372b-4b49-be57-477a45fbfee3.title: Witch
b4c814d8-372b-4b49-be57-477a45fbfee3.text:
Don't worry, deary, I can tell you just what to do and
you won't have to worry your pretty head about the
complicated bits.

a0da93fd-33e2-400d-89cf-dc1ac52182af.title: <player>
a0da93fd-33e2-400d-89cf-dc1ac52182af.text: No need to patronise me quite so much, you know.

d522c297-d2b4-4b6d-9e08-e089b3528dae.title: Witch
d522c297-d2b4-4b6d-9e08-e089b3528dae.text:
I went to anger management classes, my lambkin; that's
why I was treating you so kindly. It's either this way
of talking or I'll go back to shoving children into ovens.

d3fdaccc-b2d3-417c-a8f5-d753f1523daa.title: Witch
d3fdaccc-b2d3-417c-a8f5-d753f1523daa.text:
Just bring me 5 iron bars, though, and you're well on
the way to never having to talk to me again.

f91b14bf-fe1e-42e0-9491-5c993991d9d9.title: Witch
f91b14bf-fe1e-42e0-9491-5c993991d9d9.text:
Great, you'll go far! I made some nice painted metal
toys for you, snookums.

82ecd49f-ab99-45fe-93a9-88387fd60706.title: <player>
82ecd49f-ab99-45fe-93a9-88387fd60706.text:
Toys? Snookums? What are you on about, you
deranged old bat?

2289dfde-cc57-4ec2-9118-e6122c4ae57e.title: Witch
2289dfde-cc57-4ec2-9118-e6122c4ae57e.text:
Oh, forget it, then. If you won't react to kindness, I'm
back to luring infants into my oven. You'll have it on
your conscience.

b3ffd0fc-d04c-4690-be03-0e9069cbf2de.title: Witch
b3ffd0fc-d04c-4690-be03-0e9069cbf2de.text:
Go to the iron mine just north-east of Rimmington and
hit the bar with a plain old smithing hammer while facing
north. Then take your new magnet to Ava. Poor girl,
having to deal with whippersnappers like you.

74796ae0-0d01-43c6-863e-ceba7c6291bc.title: Witch
74796ae0-0d01-43c6-863e-ceba7c6291bc.text:
Oh, but sugarpie, I need 5 iron bars, you don't have
enough. Come back to me quickly with all 5 of them.

e689a0ba-ef30-408e-8076-10c85361ef60.title: Witch
e689a0ba-ef30-408e-8076-10c85361ef60.text:
Oh, but sugarpie, I need 5 iron bars, you don't have
any. Come back to me quickly with all 5 of them.

8f43fab7-ae56-44b0-baf5-5048cc0e5eea.title: Witch
8f43fab7-ae56-44b0-baf5-5048cc0e5eea.text:
Hoorah for you, you have the magnet. Just hand it
over to Ava. I'm working on my new recipe for spit-
roast adventurer, so disturbing me isn't wise.

7858b1cf-21ad-49f9-8587-0b4ef2cdfaf1.title: Witch
7858b1cf-21ad-49f9-8587-0b4ef2cdfaf1.text:
You were sent to try my patience, weren't you? Go
away and make that magnet, then hand it to Ava.

1baf4854-9d2e-482e-bc8f-882b7b30c699.title: Witch
1baf4854-9d2e-482e-bc8f-882b7b30c699.text:
I can't say I didn't expect this; you'd lose your head if
it weren't glued on. Lucky I made some replacements.
Take this one and leave me in peace.

6263a1d1-b10a-4250-b8d7-4399ceeee513.title: Witch
6263a1d1-b10a-4250-b8d7-4399ceeee513.text: Hello my ickle...oh, it's you. What do you want?

c4cdd6e3-6f82-4800-b40b-23c83be7d5b6.title: <player>
c4cdd6e3-6f82-4800-b40b-23c83be7d5b6.text:
I wondered whether you had anything interesting to
say.
